section#private.py-5.bg-dark.text-white
    .container.py-lg-5
        .mb-5
            p.text-uppercase.ls-2.fw-semibold.mb-2(style='color: #B08A5A;' data-i18n='events.label') Inmersiones a Medida
            h2.display-5.fw-bold.mb-4(style='max-width: 600px;')
                | Private Events &amp;
                br
                em.fst-italic(style='color: #B08A5A;') Sensory Gatherings
            p.lead.opacity-75.mb-0(style='max-width: 700px;' data-i18n='events.desc')
                | Reuniones que honran el arte de la pausa, meticulosamente coreografiadas alrededor de la narrativa del invitado. Siete d&iacute;as de aviso para curar la perfecci&oacute;n.
        .row.g-4.mb-5
            .col-md-4
                .card.h-100.bg-transparent.border-secondary.border-opacity-25.p-4.transition-hover
                    .mb-4
                        svg(width='36' height='36' viewbox='0 0 36 36' fill='none' aria-hidden='true')
                            circle(cx='18' cy='18' r='14' stroke='#B08A5A' stroke-width='1')
                            path(d='M12 18h12M18 12v12' stroke='#B08A5A' stroke-width='1.2' stroke-linecap='round')
                            circle(cx='18' cy='18' r='3' stroke='#B08A5A' stroke-width='1')
                    h3.h4.mb-3(data-i18n='events.card1.title') La Cataci&oacute;n Corporativa
                    p.text-muted.small.flex-grow-1(data-i18n='events.card1.desc')
                        | Un estudio en conexi&oacute;n. Cataci&oacute;n guiada de micro-lotes mexicanos bajo rigurosos est&aacute;ndares de competencia. Un aula viva de origen, terroir y calibraci&oacute;n de paladar.
                    .mt-3
                        span.badge.rounded-pill.border.border-secondary.text-secondary.fw-light.px-3(data-i18n='events.card1.tag') Equipos &middot; 8&ndash;20 Invitados
            .col-md-4
                .card.h-100.bg-transparent.border-secondary.border-opacity-25.p-4.transition-hover
                    .mb-4
                        svg(width='36' height='36' viewbox='0 0 36 36' fill='none' aria-hidden='true')
                            path(d='M10 26c0-4 3.58-7 8-7s8 3 8 7' stroke='#B08A5A' stroke-width='1' stroke-linecap='round')
                            circle(cx='18' cy='13' r='5' stroke='#B08A5A' stroke-width='1')
                            path(d='M7 22c0-2 1.8-4 4-4M29 22c0-2-1.8-4-4-4' stroke='#B08A5A' stroke-width='1' stroke-linecap='round')
                    h3.h4.mb-3(data-i18n='events.card2.title') Celebraciones y Reuniones
                    p.text-muted.small.flex-grow-1(data-i18n='events.card2.desc')
                        | Rituales elevados. Nuestro espacio se transforma en un santuario de caf&eacute; de especialidad con men&uacute;s progresivos adaptados a la historia de tu celebraci&oacute;n.
                    .mt-3
                        span.badge.rounded-pill.border.border-secondary.text-secondary.fw-light.px-3(data-i18n='events.card2.tag') &Iacute;ntimo &middot; Hasta 12
            .col-md-4
                .card.h-100.bg-transparent.border-secondary.border-opacity-25.p-4.transition-hover
                    .mb-4
                        svg(width='36' height='36' viewbox='0 0 36 36' fill='none' aria-hidden='true')
                            path(d='M10 28V10l8 4 8-4v18l-8-4-8 4z' stroke='#B08A5A' stroke-width='1' fill='none')
                            line(x1='18' y1='14' x2='18' y2='24' stroke='#B08A5A' stroke-width='.8' stroke-dasharray='2 2')
                    h3.h4.mb-3(data-i18n='events.card3.title') La Cata de Origen
                    p.text-muted.small.flex-grow-1(data-i18n='events.card3.desc')
                        | El ritual &quot;Pico de 14 D&iacute;as&quot;. Evaluamos granos consumidos exactamente 10&ndash;14 d&iacute;as post-tueste, en el &aacute;pice ef&iacute;mero de su complejidad arom&aacute;tica.
                    .mt-3
                        span.badge.rounded-pill.border.border-secondary.text-secondary.fw-light.px-3(data-i18n='events.card3.tag') Conocedores &middot; Cualquier Tama&ntilde;o
        .text-center
            a.btn.btn-outline-light.btn-lg.px-5.rounded-pill(href='#contact')
                span(data-i18n='events.cta') Consulta Sobre Eventos Privados
                svg.ms-2(width='14' height='14' viewbox='0 0 14 14' fill='none')
                    path(d='M2 7h10M8 3l4 4-4 4' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.5' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round')
style.
    .ls-2 { letter-spacing: 2px; }
    .transition-hover { transition: all 0.3s ease; }
    .transition-hover:hover {
        background: rgba(176, 138, 90, 0.05) !important;
        border-color: #B08A5A !important;
    }
